<br>
Here's a post about the Mini spawns:<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm25.showMessage?topicID=1328.topic">pub102.ezboard.com/fthema...1328.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
To answer your questions:<br>
<br>
1.) The &quot;safe&quot; spot I think you are referring to is on the west wall somewhere near building R.  If I understand other people's posts properly, that is where many raids used to camp.  I've never tried that particular &quot;safe&quot; spot.  Other spots people have talked about are halfway up the ramp to the 2nd floor, inside the well formed by the ramp up to the 2nd floor, and halfway up the wall in the southeast corner.  My best luck was inside the well up to the 2nd floor and have tried all of those places except the first one.  I've been killed in all those places a couple times; other times I've been lucky.  The official word from VI handed down from the /petition responses is that, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>&quot;There are no safe spots in any of the planes, just some places safer than others.&quot;</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  Good luck with scoping out the zone.  It can be done but it's still a little bit risky.<br>
<br>
2.) The opposing wall to the east minis on the 2nd floor is not safe unless there's been a raid to clear all the mobs around there.  There are Ashbone drakes that spawn near the ramp and anything from forsaken revs to clerics of innorouk to spite golems can move around up there.<br>
<br>
